ed="T" n="0795a16"/><persName key="A010785">釋崇業</persName>，不知何許人也。初同<placeName key="PL000000020095">弋陽</placeName><persName key="A008876">道岸</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0795a17"/>學毘尼<ptr type="glossary" target="#g900"/><anchor xml:id="begd1e23651"/>於<anchor xml:id="endd1e23651"/><persName key="A002468">文綱</persName>之法集。<persName key="A010785">業</persName>之服勤<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g837"/>，淬礪罔<lb
ed="T" n="0795a18"/>怠，黌肆<ptr type="glossary" target="#g169"/>之間推居元長。與<placeName key="PL000000020588">淄州</placeName><persName key="A010786">名恪</persName>齊名，<lb
ed="T" n="0795a19"/>挺拔剛毅過之，美聲洋洋達<anchor xml:id="begd1e23661"/>於<anchor xml:id="endd1e23661"/>禁闥<ptr type="glossary" target="#g339"/>。<persName key="A002461">睿宗<lb
ed="T" n="0795a20"/>聖真皇帝</persName>操心履道，勅以舊邸造<placeName key="PL000000042147">安國寺</placeName>。有<lb
ed="T" n="0795a21"/>詔<persName key="A010785">業</persName>入<placeName key="PL000000042366">承明</placeName>熏修，別殿為<ref type="person" target="#A002461">帝</ref><anchor xml:id="beg0795001"/>授<anchor xml:id="end0795001"/>菩薩戒。施<lb
ed="T" n="0795a22"/>物優渥，僉迴捨修<placeName key="PL000000042247">菩提寺</placeName>殿宇，抑由先不<lb
ed="T" n="0795a23"/>畜盈長<ptr type="glossary" target="#g825"/>之故也。<date notBefore-iso="+0713-12-26" key="j19818371992113" notAfter-iso="+0742-02-13"><name>開元</name>中</date>微疾，囑弟子曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0795a24"/>「<ref type="person" target="#A010785">吾</ref>化窮數盡，汝曹堅以防川<ptr type="glossary" target="#g340"/>，無令放逸！」語訖，<lb
ed="T" n="0795a25"/>終<anchor xml:id="begd1e23691"/>於<anchor xml:id="endd1e23691"/>所居寺之別院。<persName key="A010785">業</persName>即<persName key="A001519">南山</persName>之嗣孫矣。</p>
